title: Am I Normal: Do You Think About Death Daily?!
description:
Are you normal? Probably not. But go ahead and tell us what you do that you’re wondering if it's normal or not. We promise we won’t judge. Well, maybe we will, but we mean it in the nicest way possible.
In this case, Kristin is worried about her daily thoughts. Since the birth of her child, she now thinks about death...daily! Is she the only one who has experienced this?
